\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Study overview. Each of 101 participants completed a supervised six-minute walk test (6MWT) in the clinic and wore a hip-worn accelerometer for seven days at home. From the clinic recording we computed 51 gait features. From the home recording we detected walking bouts and computed 151 per-bout gait and activity features. The same subjects contribute to both the clinic and home analyses, so we can compare features, associations, and predictions directly.\relax }}{4}{figure.caption.1}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{fig:overview}{{1}{4}{Study overview. Each of 101 participants completed a supervised six-minute walk test (6MWT) in the clinic and wore a hip-worn accelerometer for seven days at home. From the clinic recording we computed 51 gait features. From the home recording we detected walking bouts and computed 151 per-bout gait and activity features. The same subjects contribute to both the clinic and home analyses, so we can compare features, associations, and predictions directly.\relax }{figure.caption.1}{}}
